Get name embedded for the specified .
For VB applications the transformation is like:
Resources1.resx => RootNamespace.Resources1 => Build into main assembly SubFolder\Resources1.resx => RootNamespace.Resources1 => Build into main assembly Resources1.fr.resx => RootNamespace.Resources1.fr => Build into satellite assembly Resources1.notaculture.resx => RootNamespace.Resources1.notaculture => Build into main assembly
if Resources.resx is dependent upon Class1.cs with first class fullname Namespace.Class1 => Namespace.Class1 else => RootNamespace.Resources resource file. resource file. resource name, e.g. for 'SR.ru-ru.resx' returns 'SR'.
